ing: 2 (15 ounce) cans garbanzo beans, drained and liquid reserved
des: "This hummus is creamy, nutty, and awesome! Serve with pita, veggies, or chips."
ins: Combine garbanzo beans, macadamia nuts, olive oil, onion powder, garlic powder, salt, and pepper in a high-powered blender or food processor. Cover and puree until smooth, adding the reserved liquid if necessary. Add pesto to the puree and pulse to combine.
